{"type":"message","id":"5c3ef411","parentId":"84c39dd3","timestamp":"2026-03-10T08:09:38.720Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3ad1323bb19047bfb8081965","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - 定期任务配置\n\n## 📋 每日检查（每天约 4 次）\n\n### 股票监控 ⚠️\n- **重要**: 检查自选股票是否已经到达预警范围\n- 如果有预警内容，使用 message tool 发送到飞书\n- cron 任务已在交易时间 (工作日 9:00-15:00, 每 5 分钟) 自动运行\n\n## ⚠️ 主动推送规则\n\n**立即通知**：\n- 重要/紧急邮件到达\n- <2 小时后的日程活动\n- 发现有趣或有价值的内容\n\n**保持安静 (HEARTBEAT_OK)**：\n- 深夜时段 (23:00-08:00) 除非紧急\n- 用户明显忙碌时\n- 30 分钟内已经汇报过\n\n## 🔄 记忆维护（每周一次）\n- 整理最近的 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n- 更新 MEMORY.md 中的重要信息\n\n---\n配置时间：2026-03-06 15:14\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773130178719}}
{"type":"message","id":"ae7a45c2","parentId":"5c3ef411","timestamp":"2026-03-10T08:09:52.256Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前时间是 16:09，已经过了 A 股交易时间 (15:00 收盘)。我需要获取最新的股票数据来检查是否有预警。\n\n让我获取今天 (2026-03-10) 的股票数据，看看是否有触发预警的股票。\n\n预警规则：\n1. 下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2. 上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n个股专属规则：\n- 中国石油 (601857.SH): 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警，跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n\n让我获取今天的实时数据。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"当前时间是 16:09，已过 A 股交易时间 (15:00 收盘)。让我获取今日最新数据检查预警。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_289eff4fc1c941eb9c2533e7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 初始化\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 获取今天的数据\ntoday = datetime.now()\ntrade_date = today.strftime('%Y%m%d')\nprint(f\"查询日期：{trade_date}\")\n\n# 获取 A 股实时日线数据\nts_codes = '601857.SH,601808.SH,600256.SH,600583.SH,000852.SZ,600547.SH,601069.SH,600988.SH,000975.SZ,002716.SZ,601899.SH,688111.SH'\ndf = pro.daily(ts_code=ts_codes, start_date=trade_date, end_date=trade_date)\nprint(\"=== A 股今日数据 ===\")\nif len(df) > 0:\n    print(df[['ts_code', 'close', 'pct_chg', 'pre_close', 'change']].to_string())\nelse:\n    print(\"今日数据暂未更新 (可能刚收盘或非交易日)\")\n    \n# 获取慧为智能\nbj_df = pro.daily(ts_code='920876.BJ', start_date=trade_date, end_date=trade_date)\nprint(\"\\n=== 慧为智能 ===\")\nif len(bj_df) > 0:\n    print(bj_df[['ts_code', 'close', 'pct_chg']].to_string())\nelse:\n    print(\"无数据\")\n\n# 获取美股 (苹果)\nus_df = pro.us_daily(ts_code='AAPL', start_date=trade_date, end_date=trade_date)\nprint(\"\\n=== 美股苹果 ===\")\nif len(us_df) > 0:\n    print(us_df[['ts_code', 'close', 'pct_change']].to_string())\nelse:\n    print(\"无数据\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0